# GPU Server Setup Log
# Remote: Windows PC with RTX 5090 32GB, WSL2 Ubuntu 22.04
# Date: 2026-05-19

## SSH Access
- Installed OpenSSH server on WSL2
- Initial issue: port proxy pointed to localhost instead of WSL IP (172.30.125.153)
- Fix: netsh portproxy updated to WSL internal IP
- Issue: WSL IP changes on restart, breaking port proxy
- Final fix: Installed Tailscale directly inside WSL
  - WSL Tailscale IP: 100.70.160.59 (stable)
  - SSH config on Mac: Host gpu -> 100.70.160.59, User gpu, Port 22
  - No more port proxy needed
- Passwordless sudo: /etc/sudoers.d/gpu -> gpu ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL
- SSH key auth: ed25519 key copied from Mac
- Auto-start SSH on WSL boot: /etc/wsl.conf [boot] command=service ssh start
- Start WSL headless from PowerShell: Start-Job { wsl -d Ubuntu-22.04 -- bash -c "sudo service ssh start; sleep infinity" }

## GPU / CUDA
